 All formal reports produced under this section shall be stored in the designated system of record (Redmine) and retained in accordance with the Nevada Local Government Records Retention Schedule (for a minimum of three (3) years) from the date of production.
 Report formats shall be reviewed annually by the Assistant IT Director for accuracy and utility,
